  "text": "Measures of Performances As in [CITATION_1] , we measure the performance using the Receiver Operating Characteristic (ROC) curve [CITATION_2] . Following the best practices of the field we measure the area under the ROC curve, or AUC (Area Under Curve). Loosely speaking, higher the AUC value, better the predictive performance of the algorithm.",
